 186:app_statemachine.c **** // %==========================================================================%
 187:app_statemachine.c **** // Lowest Common Ancestor (LCA) allows for the relevant exit and entry action
 188:app_statemachine.c **** // cascate occurs as needed to get between heirarchecal leafs. For a given 
 189:app_statemachine.c **** // state, walk up its parents to ROOT, then walk down to incoming state.
 190:app_statemachine.c **** // Allows for heirarchical and shared entry/exit behaviour.
